# HP Business Value and ROI Framework

## Purpose

This framework helps evaluate the business value, investment justification, and return on investment (ROI) of fulfilling a business, product, technology, inventory, procurement, infrastructure, or employee requirement.

The framework is used by:

- Leadership Teams
- Product Teams
- Customer Success Teams
- Procurement Teams
- Inventory Teams
- Finance Teams
- Operations Teams

The objective is to determine:

1. Why the requirement matters
2. What business value it creates
3. Which teams benefit
4. What business outcomes will be achieved
5. Whether the investment is justified
6. What ROI can be expected
7. Whether leadership should approve the request

---

# SECTION 1: BUSINESS VALUE ASSESSMENT

## Business Value Categories

### Productivity Improvement

Definition:

Improves employee output and reduces time required to complete work.

Examples:

- Faster AI model development
- Reduced system waiting time
- Faster deployment cycles
- Reduced manual effort

Business Impact:

- Increased employee efficiency
- Faster project completion
- Improved utilization of resources

Scoring:

| Impact | Score |
|----------|--------|
| Very High | 20 |
| High | 15 |
| Medium | 10 |
| Low | 5 |

---

### Operational Efficiency

Definition:

Improves business operations and process execution.

Examples:

- Faster procurement
- Reduced inventory delays
- Improved device deployment
- Reduced bottlenecks

Business Impact:

- Better process maturity
- Improved operational excellence
- Reduced turnaround time

Scoring:

| Impact | Score |
|----------|--------|
| Very High | 20 |
| High | 15 |
| Medium | 10 |
| Low | 5 |

---

### Innovation Enablement

Definition:

Supports innovation, AI transformation, automation, analytics, and modernization initiatives.

Examples:

- AI Engineering workstation
- Machine Learning development environment
- Advanced analytics infrastructure
- Automation platforms

Business Impact:

- Supports AI strategy
- Accelerates innovation
- Improves competitiveness

Scoring:

| Impact | Score |
|----------|--------|
| Very High | 15 |
| High | 12 |
| Medium | 8 |
| Low | 4 |

---

### Employee Experience

